				<title>Dial H for Hmmmm</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12328291/scp-3217#post-4337751</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2019 19:40:32 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Quillbit</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5550930</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like this. I am an old Dial H fan, so I may be a biased, but this was written well, and in good spirit with the inspiration material. Got my +1 easily. I would like to see some tales/data entries about instances of 3217-A, but I understand how you might feel that could distract from the original intentions.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
