				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2019 05:16:06 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>RockTeethMothEyes</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4022320</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I really enjoyed this! It's logically sound and has some very similar beats to a superhero origin story, which I personally found appealing. Took me a moment to work out the ending, but I think that's more of a fault of mine than the piece. This was an easy +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
