wiki license</p> <p>energy blast from =<a href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ab/Strange_hole_in_wall_6890.jpg">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ab/Strange_hole_in_wall_6890.jpg</a>. Will localize shortly.</p> <p>darkfalconsigil.png a combination of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:PeregrineFalconSilhouettes.svg">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:PeregrineFalconSilhouettes.svg</a> and <a href="https://www.pexels.com/photo/blank-cement-concrete-corner-984541/">https://www.pexels.com/photo/blank-cement-concrete-corner-984541/</a>, both listed as being free to use.</p> 
